{
  "texts": [
    "A synchronization problem between the SPHERES and the camera acquiring the sloshing images results in a limited validation use of the data 130.",
    "SPHERES thether-slosh (NASA) 131 Experimental test-bench to study automated strategies for steering passive cargo.",
    "It consists of two automated satellites (SPHERES) connected to two different tanks: a liquid-filled tank and a solid tank of same mass.",
    "Water The evaluation of how the fluid and solid tanks affected the closed-loop control of the tethered system can inform future development of control strategies.",
    "The results appear to indicate the correct application of control effort to reach closedloop set points."
  ]
}